        &none &none  &kp LBRC &kp RBRC &kp HASH &kp GRAVE &none                                                        &none &kp DOLLAR &kp PIPE  &kp DQT     &kp SQT  &kp BSLH     &none
        &none &kp LT &kp LPAR &kp RPAR &kp GT   &kp TILDE &none             &none    &none &none &none                 &none &kp CARET  &kp MINUS &kp EQUAL   &kp PLUS &kp COLON    &none
